===============================================================================
Monte Carlo Simulations of Schramm-Loewner Evolution curves
===============================================================================

Requirements: make, gcc, GNU argparse, and matplotlib
(for optional Python scripts)

sudo apt-get install build-essential python-matplotlib

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Usage:
make
./sle_mc -v
python ./plot/plot_xy.py ./path.csv

For further info:
./sle_mc --help

If you are running this on a computing cluster, you may find the script
run_batch.sh useful

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Released under the terms of the GNU GPL

